                                                                                        </p>
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      The following presentation was given on 24 July 2012 to the <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Devops-Brisbane/">DevOps Brisbane group</a>. Some of the technical detail about Vagrant is outdated but I think it provides a good overview of why moving to a "Infrastructure as code" setup makes a lot of sense.

